City Rat
The City Rat is the quintessential urban survivor, equally at home in Coalition
megacities and free-town black markets. Streetwise, quick-fingered, and
connected, they navigate the shadows of civilisation with ease.

City Rats begin with a solid package of criminal and social skills and have a
generous number of picks from Rogue, Technical, and Physical categories.

Attribute requirements: None. Any OCC-eligible race may choose City Rat.
Starting equipment: Street clothes, lock pick set, laser pistol or revolver,
and a network of contacts and credits.
